{"title":"石块——村笛之一","authors":["秦牧"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"石块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——村笛之一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秦牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个乡村厕所很不平常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲出来也许令人吃惊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两块踏脚石大有来历，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面都有“土地神位”的字样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个“老土地”懍于时代力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又还原为石块。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让无神论的新信徒跨在上边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思索着怎样去征服自然。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}